  "intro": {
    "eyebrow": "The Calendar",
    "title": "Community gatherings with a neighborly spirit.",
    "text": "Our Social Committee organizes a full season of neighborhood events for kids, parents, and anyone who enjoys good company. We kick things off with the Memorial Day Pool Party, featuring a DJ, live music, and a long, lazy lunch. Summer stays mellow with dive-in movie nights, and we stitch the year together with back-to-school socials, a Fall Festival, Halloween Costumes & Cocktails, and a cozy Breakfast with Santa. Watch the community messaging group for invites and sign-ups."
